svasti śrī yāṇṭu muppattoṉpatu Iyyāṇṭu muḷḷināṭṭup pira

mateyam Iḷaṅkoykkuṭi tiruppottuṭaiyabhaṭārarku Innāṭṭu

kuḷantur tavaṇirāṉ cāttaṉ Antari vaicca tiruviḷakku Oṉṟu teṉkaḷavaḻināṭṭu

māṇilai veṇmāṉiṭam Iraiyāṉ Iraiciṅkam vaicca viḷakku Oṉṟu Ivaḷ taṅkai I

raiyāṉācciya vaicca viḷakku Oṉṟu Āka viḷakku mūṉṟu Immūṉṟu viḷakkiṉukku {line partly covered by cement}

